# ===================
# Source of Truth - DO NOT IGNORE
# ===================
# The following files define contracts and must remain tracked:
# - openapi/schema.json (API contract)
# - heyapi.config.ts (SDK generation config)
# - package.json (dependencies)
# - pnpm-lock.yaml (lockfile for reproducibility)
# - .env.example (template for environment setup)

